After some googling I found the following in [official docs](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/blazor/globalization-localization?view=aspnetcore-5.0#blazor-webassembly).

I added the below tags in `.csproj` file but still no luck.

Here is my code:

**.csproj:**
